data.description: Nestled at 430 Arlington Drive in Hinesville, GA, this all brick ranch style home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and is priced affordably at $265,000. The best part? You will enjoy a substantial $5,000 contribution towards your closing costs, and there's no Homeowners' Association (HOA) to contend with. As you enter, the cozy living room welcomes you with a comforting fireplace, setting the stage for warm gatherings and relaxation. The spacious eat-in kitchen boasts abundant counter space, ideal for culinary adventures. A convenient breakfast area is perfect for casual meals, while a formal dining room awaits special occasions. The thoughtfully designed split bedroom plan ensures privacy and comfort for all occupants. Outside, the property showcases mature landscaping, creating a serene outdoor oasis. Relish bug-free evenings on the screened-in back porch, and let your pets roam freely in the securely fenced backyard. Location is a significant advantage, with easy access to shopping destinations and Fort Stewart, making daily life exceptionally convenient. Situated at the heart of Hinesville in Arlington Park, you're mere minutes away from shopping, dining, and Fort Stewart.
